data.description: AN ABSOLUTE MUST SEE! This conveniently located 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom colonial sits on 0.51 acres in the highly sought after Antrim Meadows neighbohood. Meticulously kept and within the prestigious Greencastle-Antrim school district, this gem boasts gleaming hardwood floors, granite countertops, fresh paint, new hot water heater, oversized 2 car garage, and extrememly spacious master suite that features a tray ceiling, 2 walk in closets, dual vanities, soaking tub and separate shower! The partially finished basement is the perfect space for your recreation room, home gym, additional office, or even theatre room, while the rear patio is the ideal area for your cookouts with friends. Schedule your tour for this beauty today!
